HEADWORD: daiquiri
<hw>daiquiri</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an alcoholic beverage containing
rum and lime or lemon juice, usually mixed with a fruit juice or fruit
extract and often blended with crushed ice; <as>as, a strawberry
<ex>daiquiri</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> rum cocktail.</syn>⟦br⟧
